### Testes dos novos endpoints de autenticação

# 1. Teste do Healthcheck
GET http://localhost:5092/healthcheck
Content-Type: application/json

###

# 2. Teste de validação de token (sem token - deve retornar 401)
GET http://localhost:5092/auth/validate-token
Content-Type: application/json

###

# 3. Login para obter token
POST http://localhost:5092/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "password"
}

###

# 4. Teste de validação de token (com token válido)
GET http://localhost:5092/auth/validate-token
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token_aqui}}

###

# 5. Teste com token inválido
GET http://localhost:5092/auth/validate-token
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer token_invalido_aqui

###
